      {
        "vid": "v-1774459740637",
        "title": "什一",
        "subtitle": "⌈茶室⌋的图书管理员。被拾第一次自世界覆灭中救下的，No_010世界的张可云。\n似乎因为喜欢看书而逐渐遗忘了失去家的痛苦。\n⌈茶室⌋的图书馆向来被拾翻得凌乱，有总是喜欢捧着一本书的什一帮忙，总是件好事。",
        "level": 2,
        "image": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ZZQLittleBean/Wiki-Is-She-Also-me-Who-is-So-Cute-ZZQLTB.github.io/main/wiki-data/images/char-1774459740637_v-1774459740637_card.jpg",
        "images": {
          "avatar": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ZZQLittleBean/Wiki-Is-She-Also-me-Who-is-So-Cute-ZZQLTB.github.io/main/wiki-data/images/char-1774459740637_v-1774459740637_avatar.jpg",
          "card": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ZZQLittleBean/Wiki-Is-She-Also-me-Who-is-So-Cute-ZZQLTB.github.io/main/wiki-data/images/char-1774459740637_v-1774459740637_card.jpg",
          "cover": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ZZQLittleBean/Wiki-Is-She-Also-me-Who-is-So-Cute-ZZQLTB.github.io/main/wiki-data/images/char-1774459740637_v-1774459740637_cover.jpg"
        },
        "chapterFrom": "ch-1774459320512",
        "chapterTo": "ch-1774459973949",
        "blocks": [],
        "relatedVersions": [
          "v-1774459778040"
